caption.p: Aromatic profiles of S. dentata and S. scabra flowers and leaves.

fn.p: a Compounds were present at ≥0.1% in at least one of the analyzed essential oils. exp Linear retention index relative to n-alkane on the DB5 column; lit linear retention index reported by Adams, 2007; * linear retention index reported NIST 2014 [ 24]; $ linear retention index pherobase [ 25]. Results are presented as the mean of three replicates ± SD.
